    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="记录GitHub-pages托管个人博客过程"><a href="#记录GitHub-pages托管个人博客过程" class="headerlink" title="记录GitHub pages托管个人博客过程"></a>记录GitHub pages托管个人博客过程</h1><p>由于个人的服务器上托管了其它的服务，单独拿一个服务器来托管博客网站过于浪费，所以想到在GitHub pages托管博客网站，看了很多个博客框架的介绍，最终选择Hexo作为框架进行构建，选择fluid作为默认主题。</p><hr><h2 id="GitHub"><a href="#GitHub" class="headerlink" title="GitHub"></a>GitHub</h2><p>打开<a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a>网站，点击<strong>sign up</strong>注册成功后会跳转到主界面，创建新的仓库，仓库名称必须是<strong>用户名.github.io</strong>选择<strong>public</strong>，下面选项根据个人需求选择。完成后点击<strong>Create repository</strong>，以上就完成了个人仓库的一个创建。转为新建的仓库界面，点击<strong>settings</strong>找到<strong>pages</strong>就可以看到自己的<strong>用户名.github.io</strong>显示了。此时可以点击访问，看看效果如何。</p><hr><h2 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h2><p>在安装Hexo框架之前，我们需要安装node.js，打开<a href="https://nodejs.org/en">node.js</a>网站，根据个人使用的系统下载相应的安装包，按步骤安装完成后按下<strong>win</strong>键搜索<strong>cmd</strong>在命令行中输入<code>node</code>，如果看到以下输出，说明node.js安装成功。</p><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh">`Microsoft Windows [版本 <span class="hljs-number">10.0</span>.<span class="hljs-number">19045.3758</span>]<br>(c) Microsoft Corporation。保留所有权利。<br><br>C:\Users\users&gt;<span class="hljs-keyword">node</span><br><span class="hljs-title">Welcome</span> to Node.js v20.<span class="hljs-number">9.0</span>.<br><span class="hljs-keyword">Type</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;.help&quot;</span> for more <span class="hljs-literal">inf</span>ormation.<br>\&gt;`<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下一步安装Hexo,打开<strong>cmd</strong>或者<strong>power shell</strong>，输入<code>npm install hexo-cli -g</code>根据命令操作安装完成后，在命令行中输入<code>hexo</code>,返回以下输出，说明Hexo安装成功。</p><figure class="highlight livecodeserver"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs livecodeserver">`(base) PS C:\Users\users&gt; hexo<br>Usage: hexo &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">command</span>&gt;<br><br>Commands:<br>  help     Get help <span class="hljs-keyword">on</span> <span class="hljs-title">a</span> <span class="hljs-title">command</span>.<br>  init     Create <span class="hljs-keyword">a</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">new</span> Hexo <span class="hljs-built_in">folder</span>.<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">version</span>  Display <span class="hljs-built_in">version</span> information.<br><br>Global Options:<br>  <span class="hljs-comment">--config  Specify config file instead of using _config.yml</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">--cwd     Specify the CWD</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">--debug   Display all verbose messages in the terminal</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">--draft   Display draft posts</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">--safe    Disable all plugins and scripts</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">--silent  Hide output on console</span><br><br>For more help, you can use <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;hexo help [command]&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">the</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">detailed</span> information<br><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span> you can check <span class="hljs-keyword">the</span> docs: <span class="hljs-keyword">http</span>://hexo.io/docs/`<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来在命令行打开自己想要创建博客的文件夹，输入<code>hexo init blog</code>，<u>blog可以换成自己想要的名字，最好是英文</u>，接着输入<code>cd blog</code>，转到博客目录后，输入<code>npm install</code>接下来会安装Hexo所需的组件，安装完成后输入<code>hexo server</code>，输出以下界面，Hexo安装成功，按住ctrl单击<code>http://localhost:4000</code>，成功打开Hexo。</p><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gherkin">INFO  Validating config<br>INFO  Start processing<br>INFO<br>------------------------------------------------<br>|<span class="hljs-string">                                              </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">     ________  __            _        __      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">    </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_   __  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">[  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">          (_)      </span>|<span class="hljs-string">  ]     </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_ \_</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> __   _   __   .--.</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<span class="hljs-string">  _</span>|<span class="hljs-string">    </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">[  </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> [  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">/ /&#x27;`\&#x27; </span>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">     _</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_     </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> \_/ </span>|<span class="hljs-string">, </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>||<span class="hljs-string"> \__/  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">    </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_____</span>|<span class="hljs-string">   [___]&#x27;.__.&#x27;_/[___]&#x27;.__.;__]     </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">                                              </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">       Thank you for using Fluid theme !      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">   Docs: https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/en/  </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">                                              </span>|<br>------------------------------------------------<br><br>INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000/ . Press Ctrl+C to stop.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="安装fluid主题"><a href="#安装fluid主题" class="headerlink" title="安装fluid主题"></a>安装fluid主题</h2><p>打开命令行或者终端，输入<code>npm install --save hexo-theme-fluid</code>，在所在的博客目录下创建<code>_config.fluid.yml</code>，或者直接下载<a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid/blob/master/_config.yml">_config.yml</a> ，重命名为<code>_config.fluid.yml</code>。修改 Hexo 博客目录中的 <code>_config.yml</code>。</p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm"><span class="hljs-symbol">theme:</span> fluid  <span class="hljs-meta"># 指定主题</span><br><br><span class="hljs-symbol">language:</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">zh</span>-CN  <span class="hljs-meta"># 指定语言，会影响主题显示的语言，按需修改</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在博客目录所在位置打开命令行或者终端输入以下内容，手动创建[关于页]。</p><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">page</span> about<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建成功后，编辑博客目录下 <code>/source/about/index.md</code>，添加 <code>layout</code> 属性。修改后的文件示例如下：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">about</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">layout:</span> <span class="hljs-string">about</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-string">这里写关于页的正文，支持</span> <span class="hljs-string">Markdown,</span> <span class="hljs-string">HTML</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成以上操作在命令行或者终端输入<code>hexo server</code>返回以下输出，fluid安装成功。</p><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gherkin">INFO  Validating config<br>INFO  Start processing<br><br>```<br>INFO<br>------------------------------------------------<br><br>|<span class="hljs-string">                                              </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">     ________  __            _        __      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">    </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_   __  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">[  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">          (_)      </span>|<span class="hljs-string">  ]     </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_ \_</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> __   _   __   .--.</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<span class="hljs-string">  _</span>|<span class="hljs-string">    </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">[  </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> [  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">/ /&#x27;`\&#x27; </span>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">     _</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_     </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> \_/ </span>|<span class="hljs-string">, </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>||<span class="hljs-string"> \__/  </span>|<spa